<li>90 years of experience and knowledge - you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</li>
<li>With you at every step - before during and after your holiday and we have our destination experts.</li>
<li>Flights, transfers and accommodation - included in all of our holidays.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
