  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Experience the wonders of Norway this winter. From towering peaks to rolling hills and serene fjords, there’s a slope for every type of skier/boarder, whether you're a beginner or an expert. Norway’s ski resorts, like those in <a data-udi="umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b}" title="Narvik" data-anchor="#">Narvik</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857}" title="Voss" data-anchor="#">Voss</a>, are known for their excellent snow conditions and breathtaking views. Beyond the traditional downhill skiing, Norway is also a haven for cross-country skiing and arctic activities, making it a destination for all outdoor lovers.</p>]]></listingDescription>
